ula id="hanspub.17839-formula115"><label>(3)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-2330181x27_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-2330181x28_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为以VaR为风险度量的决策者期望最大化<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-2330181x29_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-2330181x30_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>CVaR忽略利润高于某个给定水平的利润平均值，只关注利润低于该水平的情况，显得过于保守。既考虑零售商的风险又兼顾期望利润，设期望利润的权重为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-2330181x31_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>(<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-2330181x32_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>)，零售商的最大化利润-CVaR为</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.17839-formula116"><label>(4)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-2330181x33_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula></sec><sec id="s5"><title>3. 模型构建与优化</title><p>当零售商考虑接受制造商提供的价格补贴策略，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-2330181x34_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为由制造商向零售商支付的销售季节末未售出产品的单位价格补贴。然后仍以<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-2330181x35_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的处理价进行处理，根据实际意义，设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-2330181x36_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则零售商期望利润为</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.17839-formula117"><label>(5)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/2-2330181x37_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>供应商期望利润为</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.17839-formula118"><label>(6)<